   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1" image="QW_18.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Then do not hesitate. Your destiny awaits you.<BR>(You cannot proceed while you are in a party.)</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n183_cleric_jake-1-a" mid="19" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How... Why did you do it? Why?!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>I've been waiting. My brother, my friend...<BR>My dear, {user_nick}.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n183_cleric_jake-1-b" mid="21" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Truly? You have no regrets?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>It was my destiny. It was where my path led. Even now, you walk your path. Whether it's a path towards glory and virtue, or towards dread and loneliness, you must walk it. If it is truly the will of the Goddess, you will have no regrets.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n183_cleric_jake-1-c" mid="23" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I... but...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>What is there to regret? Meeting you? Becoming a Cleric? Finding a cause I believed in? Working towards a world I wanted to see? Or simply just being born into a chaotic, unforgiving world?<BR>I made my decisions, {user_nick}, and I stand by them. As you should.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n183_cleric_jake-1-d" mid="25" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How? How can I ever let this go?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>My dear Cleric. My destiny has been fulfilled. I am no more than a memory now. You must let go of this pain, and walk your path unburdened.<BR>I would never want to hold you back.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n183_cleric_jake-1-e" mid="27" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Cleric...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>Let the sadness touch your heart, and bury the resentment in your memory.<BR>Learn what you can, and then leave them. They serve no other purpose.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>Now go. Walk your path, strong and true, and you will surely find your dreams at the end. I have faith...in you.<BR>(Jake smiles earnestly, not a single shadow across his face. He turns, and fades from your memory.)</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n183_cleric_jake-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>(He smiles earnestly, not a single shadow across his face. He turns, and fades from your memory.)</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-a" mid="31" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Different...is that a good thing?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>You look like a different person now, brother. I can feel a sense of peace about you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-b" mid="33" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I would like to walk the path of a <FONT color=#a82424>Paladin</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-c" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I would like to walk the path of a <FONT color=#a82424>Priest</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-e" mid="35" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I have not made a decision yet.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Becoming different means that you have grown in some way.<BR>The peace and maturity you have gained leads me to believe you are ready for greater responsibilities. Have you made a decision about the path you would like to take?<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Once you have chosen a Specialization, your decision is permanent.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-a" mid="37" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Perhaps not...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-change_class1" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes. I am certain.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>Yes. I am certain.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-a" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Maybe not...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-change_class2" mid="41" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes. I am sure.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Oh, a <FONT color=#a82424>Priest</FONT>? The path of the Priest is one of service to others. Their magics all derive from holy light, healing and supporting others, or striking down the wicked.<BR>
Are you sure this is the path you want?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-a" mid="53" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I don't think so...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="52"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>The <FONT color=#a82424>Monk</FONT> has the strongest physical attacks among the Specializations. They usually use maces and flails, and their skills are focused around these weapons. <BR>Are you sure this is the path you want?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>I see. Come back when your doubt has passed and your path has become clear.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-g" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I, {user_nick}, humble servant of the Goddess, hear and obey.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>I pray that you remain devoted to the path that you have chosen.<BR>The Goddess has given you your destiny. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-complete_quest" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Thank you.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>I have a gift for you, to mark this occasion. It is a weapon, one that once belonged to my master. Please take it.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
